  ('h46', 'humor', 46, 'My fake plants died because I did not pretend to water them.', 'Mitch Hedberg'),
  ('h47', 'humor', 47, 'I asked God for a bike, but I know God doesn''t work that way. So I stole a bike and asked for forgiveness.', 'Emo Philips'),
