  ('h71', 'humor', 71, 'We are all the same person trying to shake hands with ourselves.', 'Unknown'),
  ('h72', 'humor', 72, 'Give a man a fish and feed him for a day. Don''t teach a man to fish and feed yourself. He''s a grown man. Fishing''s not that hard.', 'Ron Swanson (Parks and Recreation)'),
